{"type": "article", "id": 37723, "title": "Gucci托高开云集团业绩，以及，Burberry即将办雕塑大师纪念展｜浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了最重要和最好看的新闻。", "date": "2017-02-13T02:56:36Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 189, "name": "Burberry"}, {"id": 1066, "name": "Calvin Klein"}, {"id": 10635, "name": "Visvim"}, {"id": 16821, "name": "Vêtements"}, {"id": 37589, "name": "Draft Punk"}, {"id": 37590, "name": "Henry Moore"}, {"id": 2034, "name": "Dior"}, {"id": 2120, "name": "开云"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 699895, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 25, "image": "img/article/article_show/20170213102546z0ALqCsQT9g3pfRc.jpg", "contents": "<h3>一些重要的新闻：</h3><p><a href=\"http://www.cpp-luxury.com/dior-couture-sales-up-6-in-2016/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>去年，Dior 高定系列营业额上涨了 5%</b></a> |  以恒定汇率计算，Dior 的高级定制系列在去年的营业额上涨了 5% 至 19.36 亿欧元。去年一年的业绩主要受第四季度的业务驱动，在该季度的营业额上涨了 12%。Dior 目前在全世界共有 200 多家店铺，它收入的 90% 都来自于门店销售，剩下的则来自第三方分销。一些分析师预计 2017 年对于奢侈品的需求还会加速上涨，增长动力主要来自于中国国内市场的蓬勃发展，以及由于石油价格上升趋势而重新崛起的俄罗斯和中东的客户。</p><p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/business-news/financial/kering-net-profits-up-2016-strong-growth-second-half-10784730/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>开云集团公布 2016 年度财报，净利润大涨</b></a> | 开云集团的财报显示，该集团的增长主要来自于旗下品牌 Gucci 和 Yves Saint Laurent。其中，净利润同比增长 16.9%，至8.14 亿欧元。销售额同比增长 6.9%，至 123.85 亿欧元。受此消息影响，开云集团在上周五的股价上涨 2.63%，至 230.6 欧元，达到了 17 年来的最高点。</p><h3>一些值得一看的：</h3><p>在<a href=\"https://hypebeast.cn/2017/2/visvim-2017-fall-winter-collection\" rel=\"nofollow\"> 2017 秋冬纽约时装周上，日本时尚品牌 visvim 发布了男女装新系列</a>。该系列包括牛仔套装、羽绒背心和和服外套、白衬衫、Bomber Jacket、工装靴等，延续了品牌的经典美式工装和日式基调。这个系列将于今年年中开始发售。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201702131018568B6UcCSk5XIFD12d.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170213101856qJfHT1N6gvi3pRyY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201702131018563Y6wHXAZntuBh0xy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170213101856ENk8zF1dT5SBo0cL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170213101856pCOkIWeZcsFz6i7h.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170213101856KJdrYev6qC4bjgQM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.498000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170213101856r6UGKeovj0EcQIAP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170213101856sFWBopkq0fGeOcy4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170213101856l6pWq41GONZUszxQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170213101857OHTtACsrkJ6dcbPo.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170213101907wFZDncWq2HUlavSj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170213101907O7YKa910vZSoRBqc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170213101915X9ljZYC0xSdwnH2M.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170213101920wm7MO539RXEZ2rp6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>在 <a href=\"https://hypebeast.cn/2017/2/vetements-dry-cleaning-pop-up-shop-maxfield-la-closer-look\" rel=\"nofollow\">Vetements 位于洛杉矶 Maxfield 的神秘“干洗店”</a>内，有透明塑料套的羽绒外套、Oversized 西装以及 T-Shirt 多款限定服饰，另外，还有与 Dr.Martens 合作的 10 孔皮靴。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201702131019394oJMxnrbKZaRW86C.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666463\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170213101939NV6h5C9scOWxF1Yf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666463\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170213101939eZLI4nFBy8U2D3dj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666463\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170213101946zFCbARVh47mOqEjQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666463\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170213101946CpBJgov8yhXm2uYs.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666463\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>第 59 届格莱美奖开幕之前，法国电子音乐双人组<a href=\"https://hypebeast.cn/2017/2/daft-punk-first-ever-pop-up\" rel=\"nofollow\"> Daft Punk 在位于西好莱坞的 Maxfield 开设了首个期间限定店铺</a>，该店铺被划分成了一半的限定商品和一半的资料档案馆。它展出了 Daft Punk 过往的演出服、照片、艺术作品、签名式头盔以及大量从未公开的纪念品。另外还有 New Era 帽子、Medicom Toy 玩偶、KWay 外套等限定单品。这个店铺将持续至 2 月 19 日结束。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170213101958Gxmgql94MnpJ1OyI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170213101958LnHEeoW3ls0pYFJI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170213101958Sfyud725tD14zcnJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170213102005Q7ZytqlXi6mCwufs.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170213102006OI1ANm2h5BDSrwJq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201702131020065nHPUwA8Sat6FvVJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170213102005eETNQGsdz5HhB3yO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666881\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\"><a href=\"https://hypebeast.cn/2017/2/calvin-klein-2017-fall-winter-collection-raf-simons\" rel=\"nofollow\">2 月10 日， Calvin Klein 在纽约发布了 Raf Simons 担任创意总监后的首个系列</a>。该系列包括了多款宽松剪裁的西装，透明材质的橡胶外衣，与高领衫搭配的牛仔套装和皮草外套。该系列依旧是线条干净，廓形简单的 CK 风格，不过也有一些不太一样的地方，比如说它用上了红白蓝绿的醒目撞色、格纹和几何图案，Raf Simons 想要把 CK 打造成为一种年轻人喜欢的风尚。&nbsp;</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170213102025hBb0SqpTzgEZcm2w.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.502000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201702131020254Lj1NPHGDfsIhR87.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.502000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170213102025bGnpFRrwv1OlMead.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.502000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201702131020254RyrbcDm6WaMVuPi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.502000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170213102025ZsTXSql8LwERj3dc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.502000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2017021310202539aniYodBsT8VFIZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.502000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170213102025IJRmkE2VjFYyWhvl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.502000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170213102026E4ksVLopr6RGXSlB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.502000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170213102026z0gjKI2yL6GaCJdN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.502000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170213102026gHqjk1bUBTfzJcYr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.502000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170213102026UPlpWVRcQCke4fSO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.502000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201702131020269YbeIPER7j8ZU3os.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.502000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201702131020268oAj4xd2SKZJCEXY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.502000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170213102026CEgG8eqPVs4czBfi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.502000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170213102027gOxQjH4n7l58AsbL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.502000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170213102027YNnJFkR3cW50iS4H.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.502000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170213102027zny9xBLJoibVc3Th.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.502000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170213102027c5Ks4jWZRk0LUrgt.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.502000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170213102052tqSXNfPcmJR6Y1ML.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.502000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170213102052g5QKBlIqCZ9Vfkbe.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.502000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>已故的英国雕塑家  Henry Moore（1898–1986）是 20 世纪最有分量的艺术大师之一，他的抽象雕塑作品遍布世界各地。在 Henry Moore 及其家人成立，支持创新的雕塑创作、策画展览和研究活动的 Henry Moore 基金会迎来 40 周年之际，将在今年 4 月举行名为《Becoming Henry Moore》的大型展览。 </p><p><font color=\"#333332\" size=\"4\">此外，Burberry 也宣布了与 Henry Moore 基金会的合作，它计划在这个月 21 日的发布的新系列将以 </font> Henry Moore 的经典作品以及创作风格作为设计灵感。在第二场即看即买的走秀之后，会在 Makers House 会场举行 Henry Moore 的展览活动，现场将展出 40 多件雕塑品、铜像、草图模型等经典之作，并且会对以 Henry Moore 为灵感的时装作品作详细解说。 </p><p><a href=\"https://hypebeast.cn/2017/2/burberry-henry-moore\" rel=\"nofollow\">Makers House </a>的开放时间为 2 月 21 日至 27 日，地址：1 Manette Street, Soho,London。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170213102110n5jabyzESLTIJlCM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170213102125Z3IGWpjisq5e7H6w.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667107\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170213102125mC2vizMtO9dhusbG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665957\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\"><br></p><p class=\"\">题图来自：<a href=\"https://hypebeast.cn/2017/2/daft-punk-first-ever-pop-up\" rel=\"nofollow\">hypebeast</a></p>"}